{"word":"H7290 - רָדַם - râdam - raw-dam' - Sleep","slug":"H7290","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">רָדַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>râdam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>raw-dam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Sleep"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05E8;&#x05D3;&#x05DD; - ra&#x0302;dam</b> - <i>raw-dam'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>stun</i>, that is, <i>stupefy</i> (with sleep or death): - (be fast a-, be in a deep, cast into a dead, that) sleep (-er, -eth)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1719\">H1719</a>, <a href=\"#/H1721\">H1721</a>, <a href=\"#/H8639\">H8639</a>"}]}